## Development

### Environment Setup

```bash
git clone git@github.com:WayneXuCN/HostImageBackup.git
cd HostImageBackup
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Linux/macOS
.venv\Scripts\activate     # Windows
pip install -e ".[dev]"
pre-commit install
```

### Testing

```bash
pytest
```

### Formatting

```bash
black src tests
```

### Type Checking

```bash
mypy src
```

